            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-violet-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl">S</div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Storytelling Podcast</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Best choice:</strong> Framer</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2">Beautiful show notes enhance the narrative. Transcript sections for accessibility. Episode archive becomes a content library.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-violet-600 uppercase font-black">Design > Automation</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6 hover:border-violet-500 transition-colors">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-violet-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl">D</div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Daily News Podcast</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Best choice:</strong> Podpage</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2">Automatic RSS import saves hours. Daily episodes update themselves. Zero manual work required.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-violet-600 uppercase font-black">Automation > Design</p>
            </div>
